OL,3,CCould a controversial large scale
OL,4,Cbattery system be coming to your area?
OL,6,FThe batteries would store energy from
OL,7,Frenewable sources, but there are some
OL,8,Fenvironmental and safety objections
OL,9,Ffrom the communities affected. ITV
OL,10,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,12,FResearch given to ITV News shows more
OL,13,Fthan 1,000 large scale 'Battery Energy
OL,14,FStorage Systems' are being planned -
OL,15,For are already operating - in the UK.
OL,17,FThese facilities are designed to store
OL,18,Fenergy from wind and solar - but there
OL,19,Fare protests in some of the areas
OL,20,Fearmarked for such developments.
