OL,3,CCould a controversial large scale
OL,4,Cbattery system be coming to your area?
OL,6,FJust outside Diss in Norfolk, we spoke
OL,7,Fto a protester who says she is
OL,8,F"horrified" at the prospect of having
OL,9,Fone in her area.
OL,11,FOther objectors told us of their
OL,12,Fsafety concerns, especially a fear of
OL,13,Ffires.
OL,15,FThe systems can be the size of a
OL,16,Ffootball pitch and use lithium
OL,17,Fbatteries.
