OL,3,CCould a controversial large scale
OL,4,Cbattery system be coming to your area?
OL,6,FAlthough fire services say incidents
OL,7,Fare rare, there have been blazes at
OL,8,Funits in Liverpool and Tilbury, as
OL,9,Fwell as an estimated 85 around the
OL,10,Fworld.
OL,12,FWhen fires occur in these batteries
OL,13,Fthey can be hard to extinguish and can
OL,14,Flead to toxic fumes.
OL,16,FHowever, the government believes the
OL,17,Fbattery systems have a crucial role in
OL,18,Fthe journey to Net Zero.
