OL,3,CCould a controversial large scale
OL,4,Cbattery system be coming to your area?
OL,6,FThe figures, given to ITV News by
OL,7,FSolar Media Market Research, show
OL,8,F1,189 large scale battery energy
OL,9,Fstorage systems have either received
OL,10,Fplanning permission or are already
OL,11,Foperating.
OL,13,FThere are 310 planning applications in
OL,14,Fthe pipeline and 94 sites now under
OL,15,Fconstruction.
OL,17,FJosh Cornes, Solar Media Market
OL,18,FResearch, offers tips on finding out
OL,19,Fwhether a battery storage system is
OL,20,Fplanned in your area
