OL,3,CCould a controversial large scale
OL,4,Cbattery system be coming to your area?
OL,6,FThe UK government says that risks are
OL,7,Fsmall and well managed by regulations.
OL,9,FHowever fire officers are asking for
OL,10,Fchanges.
OL,12,FA spokesman for the National Fire
OL,13,FChiefs Council told ITV News: "We are
OL,14,Fengaging with government to encourage
OL,15,Fthem to create an overarching
OL,16,Fframework and UK standard for safe
OL,17,Fdeployment and operation of Battery
OL,18,FEnergy Storage Systems."
